---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Services - Bay of Islands Holiday Home Support">
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12" style="line-height: 1.6;">
    <!-- HERO / INTRO SECTION (same as index) -->
    <section
      id="home"
      style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem) 1rem;"
    >
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
        Reliable Holiday Home Support<br />
        in the Bay of Islands
      </h1>

      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.2rem; max-width: 720px;">
        I provide local oversight, changeover checks, and practical on-the-ground support
        for holiday home owners who can’t always be here themselves.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Packages Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 light-section">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Support Packages</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Essential Package -->
        <div class="bg-white text-[#111] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Essential Support</h3>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">15% Commission on Gross Rental Income</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Guest messaging (arrival, during stay, check-out)</li>
            <li>Local on-call contact for genuine issues</li>
            <li>Check-in and check-out inspections</li>
            <li>Linen and cleaning coordination</li>
            <li>Restocking of basic supplies (owner reimbursed)</li>
            <li>Coordination of urgent or routine issues</li>
            <li>Clear communication with owners</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="italic">
            Ideal for owners who self-manage bookings but need reliable local help. No commission if no bookings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Enhanced Package -->
        <div class="bg-white text-[#111] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Enhanced Property Care</h3>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">18% Commission on Gross Rental Income</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Everything in Essential</li>
            <li>Monthly full property check</li>
            <li>Exterior and garden monitoring</li>
            <li>Storm and weather response checks</li>
            <li>Maintenance coordination (non-urgent)</li>
            <li>Monthly owner update summary (with photos)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="italic">Ideal for out-of-town owners wanting proactive care.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Premium Package -->
        <div class="bg-white text-[#111] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Premium Hands-Off Support</h3>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">22% Commission on Gross Rental Income</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Everything in Enhanced Care</li>
            <li>Booking calendar oversight and inquiry responses</li>
            <li>Pricing recommendations (based on local market data)</li>
            <li>Cleaner and contractor management</li>
            <li>Priority 24/7 response</li>
            <li>Quarterly performance review</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="italic">
            Ideal for overseas or multi-property owners. (Active marketing available as add-on.)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Add-Ons Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 light-section">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Add-On Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Website & VikBooking Add-On -->
        <div class="bg-white text-[#111] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Custom Website with VikBooking Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">
            One-Off Fee: $1,500–$2,500 (depending on complexity) + Optional $50/month Maintenance
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We'll build a professional WordPress website for your holiday home, complete with VikBooking – a powerful
            booking engine that handles direct reservations from your site. It integrates seamlessly with Vik Channel
            Manager to sync availability, rates, and bookings across major channels like Airbnb, Booking.com, Expedia,
            and more.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Custom design tailored to your property</li>
            <li>VikBooking setup for independent direct bookings</li>
            <li>Channel integration for real-time sync (availability, rates, restrictions)</li>
            <li>Automated notifications for new bookings, modifications, or cancellations</li>
            <li>Basic SEO and mobile optimization</li>
            <li>Training on how to manage your site</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="italic">
            Boost direct bookings and reduce OTA fees while keeping everything centralized.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Other Add-Ons -->
        <div class="bg-white text-[#111] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Other Add-Ons</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-4">
            <li>
              <strong>Full Listing Setup & Active Marketing:</strong> +3% commission – Get your property on Airbnb,
              Bookabach, Booking.com, etc., with optimized listings.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Professional Photography:</strong> One-off $300–$500 – High-quality photos to make your listing
              stand out.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Key Safe Installation or Initial Setup:</strong> $200 – Secure access for guests and cleaners.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  
 <section class="my-16 bg-gray-100 py-10 px-6 rounded-lg">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-900">What Owners Are Responsible For</h2>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800">
    <p class="mb-6">
      While our commission covers coordination, communication, inspections, and oversight, 
      owners remain responsible for the following variable costs 
      <strong class="text-gray-900">(reimbursed at cost, no markup)</strong>:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-8 ml-4 text-gray-800">
      <li>Professional cleaning and linen hire between stays</li>
      <li>Restocking of guest supplies (e.g., toilet paper, soap, tea/coffee)</li>
      <li>Maintenance, repairs, and contractor call-outs</li>
      <li>Utilities, council rates, insurance, and other ongoing property expenses</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-800">
      Platform fees (e.g., Airbnb or Bookabach commissions) and GST are handled separately 
      by the booking channel.
    </p>
    
    <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">
      We focus on maximising your net income while keeping things transparent and hassle-free.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="text-center bg-blue-100 text-[#111] p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">Sign up now and begin your journey with us with more peace of mind.</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeYFVcX1c0UyzgJb0spkKjmGYy-z6fDWujYkBABZXxjADNC1g/viewform?usp=header" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-700">
        Sign Up Now
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
